com.moneydance.apps.md.model
Class OnlineTxn

java.lang.Object
  com.moneydance.apps.md.model.OnlineTxn
All Implemented Interfaces:
OnlineBankAcctToInterface, OnlineCCAcctToInterface, OnlinePayeeInterface
public class OnlineTxn
extends java.lang.Object
implements OnlinePayeeInterface, OnlineBankAcctToInterface, OnlineCCAcctToInterface

Simple transaction object that holds transactions that are downloaded from a bank, before the transactions can be committed to the local database. This is a very short-lived object, meant to bridge the gap between different online banking protocols and the Moneydance object model.

Method Detail

setAllowDuplicateIDs

public void setAllowDuplicateIDs(boolean allowDuplicates)
Sets whether or not this transaction is allowed to have the same FI transaction ID as another transaction that is already in an OnlineTxnList. If allowDuplicates is false, then it will not be possible to add this transaction to a list if another transaction in the list has the same FI transaction ID.
